
## Better `.gitignore`
Use this version instead of the current one:

```gitignore
# Python
__pycache__/
*.py[cod]
*$py.class

# Virtual environments
.venv/
venv/
env/

# Build / packaging
build/
dist/
*.spec
pip-wheel-metadata/

# Tooling / IDE
.vscode/
.idea/

# OS junk
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db
desktop.ini

# App runtime data
data/*
!data/.gitkeep

# Optional local settings/cache later
*.log